8. **AdminConsole.java** (line 278) - `uriInfo.getRequestUriBuilder().path("/").build()` - uses the actual request URI path with "/". **FALSE POSITIVE.**

9. **OAuthFlows.java** (lines 94, 123) - redirect is validated via `verifyRedirectUri` before being passed here. **FALSE POSITIVE.**

